    • Constructor Detail

      • Header

        public Header​(TmdFileReader tmdFile,
              int headerOffsetInFile)
       throws IOException
        Create a new header object. These objects are only created by the TMD constructor.
        Parameters:
        tmdFile - A TmdFileReader pointing to a TMD file.
        headerOffsetInFile - The offset in the TMD file, where the header is located.
        Throws:
        IOException - An error occurred while reading the TMD file.
